For any variation $\delta_\Omega$ with respect to $(\td{t}_{\alpha,k})_{\alpha \in \mathcal{P},k\geq 0}$ and $(\td{\epsilon}_i)_{1\leq i\leq g}$ (i.e. fixed log-times), we have:
